Package: RmecabKo
Type: Package
Title: Korean Text Analysis with 'MeCab'
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Junhewk", "Kim", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "junhewk.kim@gmail.com")
Description: Korean-specific part-of-speech tagging, morpheme extraction,
    content-word and noun tokenization, and morpheme-aware n-grams. The native
    'MeCab' interface and dictionary compilation are provided by 'RcppMeCab'.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    RcppMeCab (>= 0.0.1.7)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/junhewk/RmecabKo
BugReports: https://github.com/junhewk/RmecabKo/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
